1. Navigate to src folder of the Github24 from cmd terminal
2. $ python -m SimpleHTTPServer
3. open browser with localhost:8000 port

Challenge:

click on name of repository and drill in details such as who contributed to it
we need 
github username
and repository name

1. provide route: /repo/:username/:reponame
2. Template : repo.html
3. Controller: RepoController


https://api.github.com/repos/angular(username)/angular.js(reponame)
(from this display total number of issues from the repositories)
property name: "open_issues_count"

https://api.github.com/repos/angular/angular.js/contributors
then make a second call to get contributors (display image using property "avatar_url":https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/216296?v=3 )


